Royal Bank of Scotland

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Royal Bank of Scotland plc)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the retail bank. For its holding company, see Royal Bank of Scotland Group.
For the central bank of Scotland, see Bank of England.
Not to be confused with Bank of Scotland.

Royal Bank of Scotland
Banca Rìoghail na h-Alba
